as 14...UW-EC 18.5% (5-of-27) from field in 1st half...UWL leads 49-29 at end
of 3rd quarter...UW-EC cuts lead to 59-54 w/ 1:08 left...Kannel (UWL) career-
high 23 points...UWL advances to WIAC semifinals 3rd time (1st since 2011).
